@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@scenarioVersion = {{$timestamp}}

### Cadastro do usuario 1 (dono das importacoes) -> 201 sem corpo
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Maria da Silva",
  "email": "maria.imports.{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Strong@123"
}

### Login do usuario 1 -> 200 com token
# @name loginUser1
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "maria.imports.{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Strong@123"
}

### Cadastro do usuario 2 (usado para validar isolamento) -> 201 sem corpo
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Joao Pereira",
  "email": "joao.imports.{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Strong@123"
}

### Login do usuario 2 -> 200 com token
# @name loginUser2
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao.imports.{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Strong@123"
}

### Criacao de conta do usuario 1 -> 201
# @name createAccountUser1
POST {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "Carteira",
  "type": "wallet",
  "initialBalance": 0
}

### Criacao de conta do usuario 2 (para tentativa de invasao) -> 201
# @name createAccountUser2
POST {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser2.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "Carteira do Joao",
  "type": "wallet",
  "initialBalance": 0
}

### Importacao de CSV valido (usuario 1) -> 201 com importedRows=2, duplicateRows=0
# @name importCsv
POST {{baseUrl}}/imports
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----ImportBoundaryCsv
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

------ImportBoundaryCsv
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="accountId"

{{createAccountUser1.response.body.id}}
------ImportBoundaryCsv
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="extrato-exemplo.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

< ./fixtures/extrato-exemplo.csv
------ImportBoundaryCsv--

### Reimportacao do MESMO CSV (usuario 1) -> 201 com importedRows=0, duplicateRows=2
POST {{baseUrl}}/imports
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----ImportBoundaryCsvDup
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

------ImportBoundaryCsvDup
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="accountId"

{{createAccountUser1.response.body.id}}
------ImportBoundaryCsvDup
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="extrato-exemplo.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

< ./fixtures/extrato-exemplo.csv
------ImportBoundaryCsvDup--

### Importacao de OFX valido (usuario 1, conta diferente para nao colidir com fingerprint ja usado) -> 201
POST {{baseUrl}}/imports
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----ImportBoundaryOfx
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

------ImportBoundaryOfx
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="accountId"

{{createAccountUser1.response.body.id}}
------ImportBoundaryOfx
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="extrato-exemplo.ofx"
Content-Type: application/octet-stream

< ./fixtures/extrato-exemplo.ofx
------ImportBoundaryOfx--

### Importacao com accountId de outro usuario -> 404 import.account.not.found
POST {{baseUrl}}/imports
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----ImportBoundaryNotFound
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

------ImportBoundaryNotFound
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="accountId"

{{createAccountUser2.response.body.id}}
------ImportBoundaryNotFound
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="extrato-exemplo.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

< ./fixtures/extrato-exemplo.csv
------ImportBoundaryNotFound--

### Importacao com extensao nao suportada -> 422 import.format.unsupported
POST {{baseUrl}}/imports
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----ImportBoundaryUnsupported
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

------ImportBoundaryUnsupported
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="accountId"

{{createAccountUser1.response.body.id}}
------ImportBoundaryUnsupported
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="extrato-exemplo.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

data,descricao,valor
------ImportBoundaryUnsupported--

### Importacao de arquivo CSV vazio (sem linhas validas) -> 422 import.file.empty
POST {{baseUrl}}/imports
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----ImportBoundaryEmpty
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

------ImportBoundaryEmpty
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="accountId"

{{createAccountUser1.response.body.id}}
------ImportBoundaryEmpty
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="vazio.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

data,descricao,valor
------ImportBoundaryEmpty--

### Historico de importacoes do usuario 1 -> 200 com os imports criados acima
GET {{baseUrl}}/imports
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

### Historico de importacoes do usuario 2 -> 200 lista vazia (isolamento)
GET {{baseUrl}}/imports
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser2.response.body.token}}
